---
interface Props {
  realms: any[];
  fragments: any[];
  base: string;
}

const { realms, fragments, base } = Astro.props;
const safeJson = (value: unknown) => JSON.stringify(value).replace(/</g, '\\u003c');
---

<section
  class="emberline-journal"
  data-emberline-journal
  data-base={base}
  aria-labelledby="journal-title"
>
  <script type="application/json" data-journal-realms set:html={safeJson(realms)}></script>

  <header class="journal-heading">
    <div>
      <span class="rubric">memória privada · não canônica</span>
      <h2 id="journal-title">DIÁRIO DA EMBERLINE</h2>
      <p>Organize os vestígios que você realmente encontrou. Suas notas pertencem à sua leitura e nunca alteram o cânone.</p>
    </div>
    <p class="journal-privacy"><span aria-hidden="true">◇</span><strong>Somente neste navegador</strong><small>sem conta · sem envio · sob seu controle</small></p>
  </header>

  <div class="journal-summary" aria-live="polite">
    <article><strong data-journal-visited>0</strong><span>Reinos<br />registrados</span></article>
    <article><strong data-journal-notes>0</strong><span>notas<br />guardadas</span></article>
    <article class="journal-affinity"><small>Crest de Jornada</small><strong data-journal-affinity>não definido</strong><a href={`${base}/ritual/`} data-journal-ritual>realizar ritual →</a></article>
  </div>

  <div class="journal-empty" data-journal-empty>
    <span aria-hidden="true">◇</span>
    <h3>O DIÁRIO AINDA ESTÁ EM SILÊNCIO</h3>
    <p>Abra um folio territorial para registrar o primeiro vestígio. O Ritual, sozinho, não concede sigilos.</p>
    <a href={`${base}/atlas/`}>Encontrar um Reino no Atlas <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
  </div>

  <section class="journal-entries" data-journal-entries hidden aria-labelledby="entries-title">
    <header>
      <span class="rubric">ordem da sua travessia</span>
      <h3 id="entries-title">VESTÍGIOS REGISTRADOS</h3>
      <p>Escreva até 280 caracteres por Reino. O texto fica local e pode ser removido a qualquer momento.</p>
    </header>
    <ol>
      {realms.map((realm) => (
        <li data-journal-entry={realm.slug} hidden>
          <article>
            <a class="journal-entry-emblem" href={`${base}/reinos/${realm.slug}/`} aria-label={`Reabrir o folio de ${realm.realm}`}>
              <img src={`${base}/assets/emblems/${realm.emblem}`} alt="" width="256" height="256" loading="lazy" />
              <span>{String(realm.order).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
            </a>
            <div class="journal-entry-body">
              <span class="rubric" data-journal-step>vestígio</span>
              <h4>{realm.realm}</h4>
              <p>{realm.guardian} · {realm.essence}</p>
              <label for={`journal-note-${realm.slug}`}>Impressão desta travessia</label>
              <textarea
                id={`journal-note-${realm.slug}`}
                data-journal-note={realm.slug}
                maxlength="280"
                rows="3"
                placeholder="Uma memória, pergunta ou imagem que permaneceu..."
              ></textarea>
              <div class="journal-note-actions">
                <span><b data-journal-length>0</b>/280</span>
                <button type="button" data-journal-save={realm.slug}>Guardar nota</button>
                <button type="button" data-journal-clear={realm.slug}>Limpar</button>
              </div>
              <p class="journal-note-status" data-journal-status aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="journal-fragments" aria-labelledby="fragments-title">
    <header>
      <span class="rubric">recompensas de leitura · sem pontuação</span>
      <h3 id="fragments-title">FRAGMENTOS DO LIMIAR</h3>
      <p>Fundamentos já públicos reaparecem conforme sua travessia cresce. Nenhum fragmento concede poder ou informação canônica exclusiva.</p>
    </header>
    <ol>
      {fragments.map((fragment) => (
        <li data-journal-fragment={fragment.count}>
          <span class="fragment-count">{fragment.count}/19</span>
          <div>
            <small>{fragment.source}</small>
            <h4>{fragment.title}</h4>
            <p data-fragment-copy hidden>{fragment.copy}</p>
            <span data-fragment-state>adormecido</span>
          </div>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="journal-preferences" aria-labelledby="preferences-title">
    <header>
      <span class="rubric">preferências locais</span>
      <h3 id="preferences-title">MODO DE LEITURA</h3>
      <p>Estas escolhas afetam a apresentação do Codex, não o conteúdo nem sua afinidade.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="preference-grid">
      <fieldset>
        <legend>Movimento da interface</legend>
        <label><input type="radio" name="journal-motion" value="full" /> Imersivo</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="journal-motion" value="serene" /> Sereno</label>
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <legend>Escala de leitura</legend>
        <label><input type="radio" name="journal-reading" value="standard" /> Padrão</label>
        <label><input type="radio" name="journal-reading" value="expanded" /> Ampliada</label>
      </fieldset>
    </div>
    <p class="preference-status" data-preference-status aria-live="polite"></p>
  </section>

  <section class="journal-control" aria-labelledby="journal-control-title">
    <div><span class="rubric">portabilidade e controle</span><h3 id="journal-control-title">SEUS REGISTROS, SUAS REGRAS</h3><p>Exporte ou apague somente as notas do Diário. A memória territorial e o Ritual permanecem separados.</p></div>
    <div>
      <button type="button" data-journal-export>Exportar diário JSON</button>
      <button type="button" data-journal-open-clear>Apagar notas</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <dialog data-journal-clear-dialog aria-labelledby="journal-clear-title">
    <form method="dialog">
      <h3 id="journal-clear-title">Apagar todas as notas?</h3>
      <p>Esta ação remove somente <code>roc.journal.v1</code>. Reinos visitados, afinidade e preferências não serão apagados.</p>
      <div><button value="cancel">Cancelar</button><button value="confirm" data-journal-confirm-clear>Apagar notas</button></div>
    </form>
  </dialog>
</section>

<script>
  type Realm = { order: number; slug: string; realm: string; trueName: string; guardian: string; essence: string; emblem: string };
  type JournalEntry = { note: string; updatedAt: string };
  type JournalState = { version: 1; entries: Record<string, JournalEntry>; updatedAt: string | null };
  type PreferencesState = { version: 1; motion: 'full' | 'serene'; reading: 'standard' | 'expanded' };

  const EXPLORATION_KEY = 'roc.exploration.v1';
  const PILGRIMAGE_KEY = 'roc.pilgrimage.v1';
  const JOURNAL_KEY = 'roc.journal.v1';
  const PREFERENCES_KEY = 'roc.preferences.v1';
  const EMPTY_JOURNAL: JournalState = { version: 1, entries: {}, updatedAt: null };
  const EMPTY_PREFERENCES: PreferencesState = { version: 1, motion: 'full', reading: 'standard' };

  function readLocal<T>(key: string, fallback: T): T {
    try { return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(key) || 'null') || fallback; }
    catch { return fallback; }
  }

  function writeLocal(key: string, value: unknown) {
    try { localStorage.setItem(key, JSON.stringify(value)); } catch { /* armazenamento indisponível */ }
  }

  function bindEmberlineJournal() {
    const root = document.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-emberline-journal]');
    if (!root || root.dataset.bound) return;
    root.dataset.bound = 'true';
    const realms = JSON.parse(root.querySelector('[data-journal-realms]')?.textContent || '[]') as Realm[];
    const known = new Set(realms.map((realm) => realm.slug));

    const readVisited = () => {
      const exploration = readLocal<any>(EXPLORATION_KEY, null);
      return Array.isArray(exploration?.visited)
        ? [...new Set<string>(exploration.visited.filter((slug: unknown): slug is string => typeof slug === 'string' && known.has(slug)))]
        : [];
    };
    const readJournal = (): JournalState => {
      const journal = readLocal<any>(JOURNAL_KEY, EMPTY_JOURNAL);
      if (journal?.version !== 1 || typeof journal.entries !== 'object') return { ...EMPTY_JOURNAL, entries: {} };
      const entries = Object.fromEntries(Object.entries(journal.entries).filter(([slug, entry]) => known.has(slug) && typeof (entry as any)?.note === 'string')) as Record<string, JournalEntry>;
      return { version: 1, entries, updatedAt: typeof journal.updatedAt === 'string' ? journal.updatedAt : null };
    };

    const render = () => {
      const visited = readVisited();
      const journal = readJournal();
      const notes = Object.values(journal.entries).filter((entry) => entry.note.trim()).length;
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-visited]')!.textContent = String(visited.length);
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-notes]')!.textContent = String(notes);
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-empty]')!.hidden = visited.length > 0;
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-entries]')!.hidden = visited.length === 0;

      root.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-entry]').forEach((item) => {
        const slug = item.dataset.journalEntry || '';
        const step = visited.indexOf(slug);
        item.hidden = step < 0;
        item.style.order = String(step);
        const marker = item.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-step]');
        if (marker && step >= 0) marker.textContent = `travessia ${String(step + 1).padStart(2, '0')}`;
        const textarea = item.querySelector<HTMLTextAreaElement>('[data-journal-note]');
        if (textarea && document.activeElement !== textarea) textarea.value = journal.entries[slug]?.note || '';
        const length = item.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-length]');
        if (length) length.textContent = String(textarea?.value.length || 0);
      });

      root.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-fragment]').forEach((fragment) => {
        const awake = visited.length >= Number(fragment.dataset.journalFragment);
        fragment.classList.toggle('is-awake', awake);
        const copy = fragment.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-fragment-copy]');
        const state = fragment.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-fragment-state]');
        if (copy) copy.hidden = !awake;
        if (state) state.textContent = awake ? 'desperto' : `requer ${fragment.dataset.journalFragment} sigilo${fragment.dataset.journalFragment === '1' ? '' : 's'}`;
      });

      const pilgrimage = readLocal<any>(PILGRIMAGE_KEY, null);
      const affinity = root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-affinity]')!;
      const ritualLink = root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-ritual]')!;
      if (pilgrimage?.version === 1 && typeof pilgrimage.primary === 'string' && typeof pilgrimage.secondary === 'string') {
        affinity.textContent = `${pilgrimage.primary} × ${pilgrimage.secondary}`;
        ritualLink.textContent = 'reabrir leitura →';
      } else {
        affinity.textContent = 'não definido';
        ritualLink.textContent = 'realizar ritual →';
      }
    };

    root.querySelectorAll<HTMLTextAreaElement>('[data-journal-note]').forEach((textarea) => {
      textarea.addEventListener('input', () => {
        const length = textarea.closest('[data-journal-entry]')?.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-length]');
        if (length) length.textContent = String(textarea.value.length);
      });
    });

    root.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>('[data-journal-save]').forEach((button) => {
      button.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const slug = button.dataset.journalSave || '';
        if (!readVisited().includes(slug)) return;
        const item = button.closest<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-entry]')!;
        const textarea = item.querySelector<HTMLTextAreaElement>('[data-journal-note]')!;
        const journal = readJournal();
        const note = textarea.value.trim().slice(0, 280);
        if (note) journal.entries[slug] = { note, updatedAt: new Date().toISOString() };
        else delete journal.entries[slug];
        journal.updatedAt = new Date().toISOString();
        writeLocal(JOURNAL_KEY, journal);
        item.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-status]')!.textContent = note ? 'Nota guardada neste navegador.' : 'Nota vazia removida.';
        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('roc:journal-updated'));
        render();
      });
    });

    root.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>('[data-journal-clear]').forEach((button) => {
      button.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const item = button.closest<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-entry]')!;
        const textarea = item.querySelector<HTMLTextAreaElement>('[data-journal-note]')!;
        textarea.value = '';
        textarea.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'));
        item.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-journal-status]')!.textContent = 'Campo limpo. Use “Guardar nota” para confirmar.';
        textarea.focus();
      });
    });

    const preferences = readLocal<PreferencesState>(PREFERENCES_KEY, EMPTY_PREFERENCES);
    root.querySelectorAll<HTMLInputElement>('input[name="journal-motion"]').forEach((input) => { input.checked = input.value === preferences.motion; });
    root.querySelectorAll<HTMLInputElement>('input[name="journal-reading"]').forEach((input) => { input.checked = input.value === preferences.reading; });
    root.querySelectorAll<HTMLInputElement>('input[name="journal-motion"], input[name="journal-reading"]').forEach((input) => {
      input.addEventListener('change', () => {
        const state: PreferencesState = {
          version: 1,
          motion: (root.querySelector<HTMLInputElement>('input[name="journal-motion"]:checked')?.value || 'full') as PreferencesState['motion'],
          reading: (root.querySelector<HTMLInputElement>('input[name="journal-reading"]:checked')?.value || 'standard') as PreferencesState['reading'],
        };
        writeLocal(PREFERENCES_KEY, state);
        document.documentElement.dataset.rocMotion = state.motion;
        document.documentElement.dataset.rocReading = state.reading;
        root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-preference-status]')!.textContent = 'Preferência aplicada ao Codex.';
        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('roc:preferences-updated', { detail: state }));
      });
    });

    root.querySelector<HTMLButtonElement>('[data-journal-export]')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const payload = { exportedAt: new Date().toISOString(), journal: readJournal(), exploration: readLocal(EXPLORATION_KEY, null), pilgrimage: readLocal(PILGRIMAGE_KEY, null), preferences: readLocal(PREFERENCES_KEY, EMPTY_PREFERENCES) };
      const href = URL.createObjectURL(new Blob([JSON.stringify(payload, null, 2)], { type: 'application/json' }));
      const link = document.createElement('a'); link.href = href; link.download = 'diario-da-emberline.json'; link.click(); URL.revokeObjectURL(href);
    });

    const dialog = root.querySelector<HTMLDialogElement>('[data-journal-clear-dialog]')!;
    root.querySelector<HTMLButtonElement>('[data-journal-open-clear]')?.addEventListener('click', () => dialog.showModal());
    root.querySelector<HTMLButtonElement>('[data-journal-confirm-clear]')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      try { localStorage.removeItem(JOURNAL_KEY); } catch { /* armazenamento indisponível */ }
      window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('roc:journal-updated'));
      render();
    });

    window.addEventListener('roc:realm-visited', render);
    window.addEventListener('roc:exploration-reset', render);
    window.addEventListener('roc:pilgrimage-updated', render);
    window.addEventListener('storage', render);
    render();
  }

  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', bindEmberlineJournal);
</script>

<style>
  .emberline-journal { width: min(1320px, calc(100% - 4rem)); margin-inline: auto; padding-bottom: 8rem; }
  .journal-heading { display: flex; align-items: end; justify-content: space-between; gap: 3rem; padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem) 0 2rem; }
  .journal-heading > div { max-width: 760px; }
  .journal-heading h2, .journal-entries h3, .journal-fragments h3, .journal-preferences h3, .journal-control h3 { margin-top: .55rem; color: var(--parchment); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4.2vw, 3.5rem); }
  .journal-heading p, .journal-entries header p, .journal-fragments header p, .journal-preferences header p, .journal-control p { margin-top: .8rem; color: var(--parchment-dim); }
  .journal-heading .rubric, .journal-entries .rubric, .journal-fragments .rubric, .journal-preferences .rubric, .journal-control .rubric { color: var(--gold); }
  .journal-privacy { display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; min-width: 240px; padding: .9rem 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--edge); }
  .journal-privacy > span { grid-row: 1 / 3; margin-right: .7rem; color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .journal-privacy strong { color: var(--parchment); font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 500; }
  .journal-privacy small { color: var(--parchment-faint); font-size: .65rem; }
  .journal-summary { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 2fr; border: 1px solid rgba(201,163,92,.32); background: var(--codex); }
  .journal-summary article { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; min-height: 118px; padding: 1.5rem; border-right: 1px solid var(--edge); }
  .journal-summary article:last-child { border-right: 0; }
  .journal-summary > article > strong { color: var(--gold); font: 2.8rem var(--font-display); }
  .journal-summary > article > span { color: var(--parchment-dim); font-size: .78rem; line-height: 1.25; }
  .journal-summary .journal-affinity { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: .25rem 1rem; }
  .journal-affinity small { color: var(--parchment-faint); }
  .journal-summary .journal-affinity strong { color: var(--parchment); font: 1rem var(--font-display); text-transform: uppercase; }
  .journal-affinity a { grid-row: 1 / 3; grid-column: 2; align-self: center; color: var(--gold); font-size: .72rem; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .journal-empty { display: grid; justify-items: center; margin-top: 2rem; padding: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem); border: 1px dashed rgba(201,163,92,.28); text-align: center; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,163,92,.06), transparent 55%); }
  .journal-empty[hidden], .journal-entries[hidden], [data-journal-entry][hidden] { display: none; }
  .journal-empty > span { color: var(--gold); font-size: 2rem; }
  .journal-empty h3 { margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--parchment); }
  .journal-empty p { max-width: 580px; margin: .8rem 0 1.4rem; color: var(--parchment-dim); }
  .journal-empty a { color: var(--gold); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .journal-entries, .journal-fragments, .journal-preferences { padding-top: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem); }
  .journal-entries > header, .journal-fragments > header, .journal-preferences > header { max-width: 760px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .journal-entries h3, .journal-fragments h3, .journal-preferences h3, .journal-control h3 { font-size: clamp(1.55rem, 3.6vw, 2.8rem); }
  .journal-entries ol { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; padding: 0; list-style: none; }
  .journal-entries li article { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 150px 1fr; border: 1px solid var(--edge); background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,163,92,.05), var(--codex)); }
  .journal-entry-emblem { position: relative; display: grid; place-items: center; min-height: 240px; overflow: hidden; border-right: 1px solid var(--edge); background: #090806; }
  .journal-entry-emblem img { display: block; width: min(112px, calc(100% - 2rem)); height: auto; aspect-ratio: 1; object-fit: contain; opacity: .8; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 18px rgba(201,163,92,.14)); }
  .journal-entry-emblem span { position: absolute; right: .7rem; bottom: .55rem; color: var(--gold); font: .65rem var(--font-display); }
  .journal-entry-body { padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem; }
  .journal-entry-body h4 { margin-top: .2rem; color: var(--parchment); font-size: 1.35rem; }
  .journal-entry-body > p { color: var(--parchment-faint); font-style: italic; }
  .journal-entry-body label { display: block; margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--parchment-dim); font-size: .72rem; }
  .journal-entry-body textarea { width: 100%; margin-top: .35rem; padding: .8rem; resize: vertical; border: 1px solid var(--edge); color: var(--parchment); background: rgba(0,0,0,.24); font: .95rem/1.5 var(--font-body); }
  .journal-entry-body textarea:focus { border-color: var(--gold); outline: 2px solid rgba(201,163,92,.16); outline-offset: 2px; }
  .journal-note-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; gap: .55rem; margin-top: .5rem; }
  .journal-note-actions span { margin-right: auto; color: var(--parchment-faint); font-size: .65rem; }
  .journal-note-actions button, .journal-control button, dialog button { padding: .55rem .8rem; border: 1px solid var(--edge); color: var(--parchment-dim); background: transparent; font: .66rem var(--font-display); letter-spacing: .07em; text-transform: uppercase; cursor: pointer; }
  .journal-note-actions button:hover, .journal-control button:hover, dialog button:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
  .journal-note-status { min-height: 1.2em; margin-top: .4rem; color: var(--gold) !important; font-size: .7rem; font-style: normal !important; }
  .journal-fragments ol { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1rem; padding: 0; list-style: none; }
  .journal-fragments li { min-height: 250px; padding: 1.2rem; border: 1px solid var(--edge); color: var(--parchment-faint); background: rgba(0,0,0,.18); }
  .fragment-count { color: var(--parchment-faint); font: .7rem var(--font-display); }
  .journal-fragments li small { display: block; margin-top: 2.4rem; color: var(--parchment-faint); }
  .journal-fragments li h4 { margin-top: .4rem; color: var(--parchment-dim); font-size: 1rem; }
  .journal-fragments li p { margin-top: .8rem; color: var(--parchment-dim); line-height: 1.5; }
  .journal-fragments li [data-fragment-state] { display: block; margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--parchment-faint); font-size: .66rem; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .journal-fragments li.is-awake { border-color: rgba(201,163,92,.5); background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(201,163,92,.1), var(--codex)); box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px rgba(255,122,61,.03); }
  .journal-fragments li.is-awake .fragment-count, .journal-fragments li.is-awake [data-fragment-state] { color: var(--gold); }
  .journal-fragments li.is-awake h4 { color: var(--parchment); }
  .preference-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  .preference-grid fieldset { padding: 1.2rem; border: 1px solid var(--edge); }
  .preference-grid legend { padding: 0 .4rem; color: var(--gold); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: .72rem; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .preference-grid label { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .45rem; margin: .4rem 1.2rem .2rem 0; color: var(--parchment-dim); }
  .preference-grid input { accent-color: var(--gold); }
  .preference-status { min-height: 1.4em; color: var(--gold); font-size: .72rem; }
  .journal-control { display: flex; align-items: end; justify-content: space-between; gap: 2rem; margin-top: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem); padding: 1.6rem; border: 1px solid var(--edge); }
  .journal-control > div:first-child { max-width: 760px; }
  .journal-control > div:last-child { display: flex; gap: .6rem; flex: 0 0 auto; }
  dialog { width: min(520px, calc(100% - 2rem)); padding: 0; border: 1px solid var(--gold); color: var(--parchment); background: var(--codex); }
  dialog::backdrop { background: rgba(0,0,0,.78); backdrop-filter: blur(5px); }
  dialog form { padding: 1.5rem; }
  dialog h3 { color: var(--parchment); }
  dialog p { margin: .8rem 0 1.2rem; color: var(--parchment-dim); }
